  "body": "### Description\n\nThere are no opportunities to redirect to another resource in graphQL response. For example, if authentication request succeeds, redirect user to their profile and if not, redirect them again to registration page.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\nTo my mind, the most native way to implement this feature would be to allow adding custom status codes to successful responses(3xx in this case) without force overriding them in [this class](https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/main/extensions/smallrye-graphql/runtime/src/main/java/io/quarkus/smallrye/graphql/runtime/SmallRyeGraphQLExecutionHandler.java).  ",
